</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Reversing stock for returns belonging to orders including delivery orders</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>The procedure for reversing stock is the same for returns belonging to orders that include delivery orders. The editing window displayed during the stock reversal shows whether there are delivery orders.</p>
</div>
