<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Tip: Changing values</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Some entries can be changed. Such entries either include a drop-down list or a <strong>pencil</strong> icon. Click on the pencil icon to edit the parameter.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
